column5: Amazing they got that shaft right into the end of the cavern the trapped miners were in. Pretty sure I shed a tear about the time the guys son broke down... not sure... hope nobody got any video of that.
Same here, but I wasn't going to admit that
Its amazing. Not really sure what else to say.
CHI-CHI-CHI!!  LE-LE-LE!     VIVA los MINEROS DE CHILE!!!    (a little chant that you might hear during the tv broadcasts).    Finally nice to see a feel good story instead of something depressing.
